WEBVTT

00:01.200 --> 00:02.800
Since there's a river to the west

00:03.440 --> 00:04.480
And grass on the hills

00:05.320 --> 00:06.680
The Wuzhao's main force is cavalry

00:07.320 --> 00:08.040
Their warhorses

00:08.680 --> 00:09.440
Are like their wives

00:09.880 --> 00:10.280
And sons

00:11.120 --> 00:11.480
So

00:12.320 --> 00:13.520
Their main force should be in the west

00:14.680 --> 00:15.920
To avoid the enemy's main force

00:16.280 --> 00:16.680
Tonight

00:17.240 --> 00:17.880
Raid the eastern camp

00:18.840 --> 00:19.160
Brother-in-law

00:20.000 --> 00:21.200
I ask to lead the cavalry out of the city

00:21.840 --> 00:23.440
They are all brothers who have followed me

00:23.800 --> 00:24.920
Since I joined the army

00:25.480 --> 00:26.680
Each willing to fight to the death
